In re: Price 64A16-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2016 William Gerald Price, for Price, William Gerald. Natasha M. Barone, Attorney at Law, Fayetteville, for Federal National Mortgage Association.

J. Scott Flowers, Attorney at Law, Fayetteville.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 11th of July 2016 by Respondent to Reconsider:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th of August 2016."
